Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:20.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よしっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:57.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,マスミ　あんたどこ行ってたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,マスミ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やだ　なにこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:35.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,水の音？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,娘の…様子かい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:01.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,確かに　この頃体調を崩しちまってるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:05.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なに　原因は分かってるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:09.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,医者にも蟲師にも直せねえ病さ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:13.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ついた男が会いに来なくなったってんでね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,気が塞いじまって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:19.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,体の具合まで悪くなっちまったんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,毎度のことじゃあるんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:27.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今回のは随分長引いてでね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　それは気の病だけとは限りませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:36.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,と言いますと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:41.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつ　水盤を用意しちゃもらえませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これに姿を映してみてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:01.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,影を　映し取られたんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:08.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,波のない池に棲む　「水鏡」という蟲がいましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もとは水銀のような姿をしたものですが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,池の水面に動物の姿が映り込むと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その姿をまねて　陸に上がります
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして本体の後に付いて回る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:29.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すると　本体の方は少しずつ体力が衰えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:35.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本体が衰えるほど　水鏡は実体を持ち始め
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:38.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本体は実体を失っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そしてやがては　水鏡は本体に成り代わる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:48.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,水鏡は水の中の鉱物質を必要とし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:52.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,実体を持つと　より濃度の高い水を求めて歩き回る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,水鏡はもともとの姿では自ら動くことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:03.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だから　自由に動ける体を欲しがるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それは困る　なんとかならんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本体と入れ替わる瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰の目にも水鏡の姿が見える
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:16.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そこを本体に鏡に映されると
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,姿は崩れ　本体も元に戻ります
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだ　簡単なことじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　マスミ　お前　手鏡持ってただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:27.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこやった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだ　曇っちまってるんじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:35.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,研いでやるから　貸して
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:40.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やめてよ　大事な　鏡なの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,自分でやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ごめん　ちょっと出てくる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　どこ行くのよ　マスミ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また随分曇ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:01.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたに研いでほしいから　自分じゃ研がないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あのさ　マスミ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このところ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここいら一帯すっかり鏡研ぎの口も減っちまってな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:21.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,仕事場変えてみようと思うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな　じゃ次はいつ会えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:31.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあな　いつ戻るか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,嫌よ　そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:39.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺だって嫌だけど　でも食ってかなきゃならねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:41.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,分かってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　じゃ私　あんたの里で待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたの嫁になる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:51.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,所帯を持つ気はまだねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら　その気になるまで待つよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:54.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おめえみてえな跳ねっ返りの嫁はごめんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,嫁にするなら　もっと大人しい娘がいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そういうわけだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,次の約束はできねえからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今度鏡が曇ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,悪いが　自分が研いでくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何やってんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そこにいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんた　あたしになりたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こんなあたしになりたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:45.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さんにも　水鏡の足音が聞こえ始めたか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,手鏡は研いだか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつに成り代わられたくなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,早いとこ研いどけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:03.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,別に代わってやったっていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:04.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私はもう私でいたってしかたない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:10.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほしいならあげたっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:17.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あのな　投げ遣りにしてと後悔することもできなくなるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:19.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,水鏡と入れ替わるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,自我も実体も失うってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は自分の意志で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:29.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この世に影響を及ぼすことが何一つできないものになるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:37.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いても　いなくても　同じものに…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:50.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら　今の私と同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:58.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの人にとって　私はそれくらい軽いものだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:03.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私が何を言ったって　何をしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんの影響も受けやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:14.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,実体があってもなくても同じこと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そこは　さびしいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:33.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だがな　そこよりずっとさびしい所がある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:38.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲と同じ実体をもたないものたちの棲む世だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:45.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そこは　この世には必要とされないものたちの蠢く暗い所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:50.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲どもに心なんぞはありはしないが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,多くのものが光を求めて這い出そうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなさびしい所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:08.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,相手は実体に姿を映されただけで消えるはかないものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:15.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,血の通う実体を持つということは　それだけで強い力を持つってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:22.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　一旦入れ替わると　それも逆転する
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:30.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また暖かい場所へ戻りたければ　自分の身は自分で守るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,脈が弱い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,鏡は研いだか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:51.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よし　肌身離さず持ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:55.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じき　水鏡が姿を現す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その瞬間を鏡に映すんだ　見逃すな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お手洗い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一人で大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,戻ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんな所に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,体が…動かない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,入れ替わられちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:56.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんなふうに人の周りを付いて回るだけのものになるの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:18:59.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いやだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなの　さびしすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:05.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何よ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:09.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,真似してんじゃないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:46.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当にもうなんともないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何言ってんだ　このバカ娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今日一日くらい大人しくしてなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんで消えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　俺もずっと考えてんだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか　眼だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前の眼に水鏡の姿が映ったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:18.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだ　眼を開けてさえいりゃ　鏡なんか必要ねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やはり実体を持って生きてるってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それだけで充分力を持ってんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうかしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:33.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今まで気が付かなかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:36.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんた　よく見ると男前だね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,髪の色とか変だけと　血筋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,奥さんいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,郷里はどこ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当にもう治ったみたいですな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さようで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　俺はこの辺で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう少しゆっくりしてきなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お礼もしたいしさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:57.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,マスミ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前　少しは懲りんか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:42.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やはり元の場所に戻ってたか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,付いて来い　もっと山深い池に案内してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,実体はくれてやらんがな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:56.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなさびしそうにしてるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,花惑い
